Flat Style::title

This page shows that if your needs are simple, you can use a "flat" style of structuring the document. As the top level node is implicit a md node, you can just write paragraphs of text like this. If you need headings, you can use the h node, like so:

This is a heading::h

Assuming that all you need are a few heading/divisions in your doucment, you don't have to indent at all!

